00:32:52.630 --> 00:32:53.955
Itu lucu.

524
00:32:55.500 --> 00:32:56.925
Kita akan bertemu lagi.

525
00:33:01.540 --> 00:33:02.697
Ibu.

526
00:33:03.640 --> 00:33:05.333
