00:39:36.870 --> 00:39:38.626
Aku ingin pergi ke Biro Pengunjung Guam.

631
00:39:38.740 --> 00:39:41.662
Naiklah mobil antar-jemput 
gratis ke sana,

632
00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:43.898
